channel.title: Autospawn.cfg
channel.description:
Ok look, I am adding new and more complex areas, and sometimes I add NPC's and then shops don't work. Like one time added a bunch of Jads and those thox-zom or watever in this one place, but shops don't work...So here's my questions, is the NPC just bugged? Or as I heard my Autospawn.cfg is too big?? I just counted the lines and I have...511NPC's and it takes up ten pages by Microsoft Word, so if you know what to do please tell me, and if it true that it doesn't work with those other NPC's, and when I remove the NPC's the shops work, then do I make like Autospawn2.cfg or something? If you know please post how to or if there is a tutorial :D
Thx :P MinimiGuard
